1. **Collection**: 2-minute timed sessions with real-time visualization
2. **Filtering**: Moving average filters to reduce noise
3. **Export**: Data saved as CSV files locally
4. **Upload**: CSV uploaded to Firebase Storage
5. **Processing**: Jetson Nano performs AI analysis
6. **Results**: Processed results displayed in the app

